seo: JBoss,漏洞检测,CVE-2017-12149,反序列化漏洞
summary: 该插件用于检测JBoss 5.x/6.x是否存在CVE-2017-12149反序列化漏洞，通过发送特定payload验证漏洞是否存在。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether JBoss 5.x/6.x has the CVE-2017-12149 deserialization vulnerability by sending a specific payload to verify the existence of the vulnerability.
